[normal]It is the polic
[normal]y of Public Health England (PHE) to work in co-operation with the pharmaceutical, biotechnology, vaccine, diagnostic, and other healthcare-related industries in order to facilitate the development of products and technologies beneficial to health. Health p
[normal]rotection consultancy services are also provided to a wide range of companies. These relationships are managed on an arms-length, contractual and commercial basis, including the charging of fees under standard terms and conditions. In this context, PHE mai
[normal]ntains active relationships with a broad range of companies in the UK and internationally. PHE has a comprehensive system for managing conflicts of interest.
